    "ultimate": {
      "name": "Primal Wrath",
      "description": "(Passive:) When inside Phylax, Edith can accumulate Wrath according to the damage she receives (calculated before damage reduction). (Active:) Edith ejects herself forward from Phylax, knocking back nearby enemies. After that, she takes flight and can perform ranged Basic Attacks, each dealing 35( +75% Total Physical Attack) (+25% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage). Edith also gains new skills in this state. When in flight, Edith gains 350( +5% Total HP)-350( +20% Total HP) extra Shield, 50%-150% extra Attack Speed and 5%-20% Hybrid Lifesteal based on the Wrath she accumulated, and converts each point of (Extra Physical Defense) and (Extra Magic Defense) into 3.2 (Magic Power). The flight state lasts up to 8s.",
